Kaspɩyɛnii teŋgu kɛna lɩm wadaɣsɔsɔɣa nakɩyɩ nɛ kɛwɛ [[Aazii tɛtʋ wandamm|Azii]] wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ taa. Lɩm pɔɔ ŋga payaɣ-kɛ se [[Fɔlɩka Pɔɔ|Vɔlga]] yɔ, ka-taa lɩm kpeŋna kɩ-taa. Wisi ɖɩlyɛ nɛ wɩsɩ ɖʊyɩ taa lɛ, Azii hɛkʊ nɛ hɛkʊ taa kataŋga sɔsɔɣa nakɩyɛ kɛ teŋgu kʊnɛ kɩzɩna kamaɣ piyele wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ taa nɛ hadɛ kiŋ ɖɔɖɔ ɛlɛ, kokaazi nɛ Ɛlburzi piisi ñɛwɛna. 
[[File:View_of_Baku,_2004_(2).jpg|thumb|Vue de Baku 2004]]

Ajɛya wena acɔ teŋgu kʊnɛ nɛ kɩtaa yɔ, anaa yɔ: wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ nɛ sɩ-hayʊ kiŋ ɛlɛ [[Kazakisitanɩ|Kazakistanii]], wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ nɛ sɩ-hadɛ kiŋ ɛlɛ [[Turkimenistanɩ|Turkimenistanii]] piyele haɖɛ kiŋ kpaagbaa ɛlɛ Iiraŋ tɛtʊ pɩkazɩ nɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ nɛ sɩ-hadɛ kiŋ ɛlɛ [[Azɛrbayɩjanɩ|Azɛrbayijanii]] nɛ wɩ;sɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ nɛ sɩ-hayʊ kiŋ ɛlɛ, [[Ruusii|Ruusi]] ɛjaɖɛ. Teŋgu kʊnɛ kɩwɛɛ kɩkpɩyʊ nɛ kɩkpɩyʊ mbʊ pɔyɔɔ yɔ, tɩŋ fɛyɩ nɛ wɩsɩ ñakɩlɩʊ ñaaʊ.
[[File:TurkmenbashiSea.jpg|thumb|Turkmenbashi Teŋgu]]

Kaspɩyɛnii teŋgu kʊnɛ kɩ-walanzɩ mɩtaɖɛ wɛ 371 000km2 piyele kɩ-ɖaalakɩŋ taa maɣna kilomɛtanaa 1030 nɛ kɩ-walanzɩ taa ñɛwɛ kilomɛtanaa 435. Pamaaza-kʊ koko nɛ pata ɛlɛ pɩwɛ kilomɛtanaa 7 000 nɛ kɩ-tɛ cukaŋ taa wɛ mɛtanaa ɛzɩ 1025. Teŋgu kʊnɛ kɩpaɣlika taa wɛ ɛzɩ 78 200 km3  yɔ.
